
Create Self-Signed Certificates
$cd [glassfish home directory]/glassfish/domains/domain1/config

$keytool -genkey -v -alias admincert -keyalg RSA -storetype PKCS12 -keystore client_keystore.p12 -storepass changeit -keypass changeit


Import Certificate in GlassFish trust store

$keytool -export -alias admincert -keystore client_keystore.p12 -storetype PKCS12 -storepass changeit -rfc -file selfsigned.cer
$keytool -import -file selfsigned.cer -keystore cacerts.jks -alias admincert -storepass changeit



